Summary: During the past 18 months of the COVID pandmeic, we’ve all become armchair epidemiologists. Those with quantitative minds and python capabilities may want to “crunch the numbers” in a way that goes beyond widely-used web dashboards. This post walks through how to download, prepare, and analyze a rich historical dataset using the COVID Act Now API.